review_blob: If you like wine coolers/flavored malt beverages, TRY IT!! If you like BEER, you probably wont like it. Ive tried a lot of different malt beverages and this one takes the cake!! Easy drinking... must be careful as it is 8%abv. Cant taste alcohol at all! Im a fan of amber ales- spouse likes Bud Light but we both agree on this one!
beer_name: Steel Reserve Alloy Series Blk Berry 211
